to play a bit with
the value of the food,

00:07:43.262 --> 00:07:45.731 align:start size:91% position:9%
-so we'll start with their
regular monkey chow.
-Right.

00:07:45.764 --> 00:07:48.934 align:start size:91% position:9%
Which they see a couple times
a day on a daily basis.

00:07:48.967 --> 00:07:52.771 size:84% position:58% line:0%
And then we'll see what
happens when we introduce
that nice, tasty peanut.

00:07:52.804 --> 00:07:54.573 size:84% position:58% line:0%
[Cecile speaking]

00:07:54.606 --> 00:07:57.276
[Michael] Right. And so, I'm
assuming they like peanuts.

00:07:57.309 --> 00:08:01.046 align:start size:88% position:13%
-Right, so--
-They don't like peanuts
in or on poop.

00:08:01.079 --> 00:08:03.583 align:start size:72% position:28%
