that he is going to pair
with the replica feces

00:08:17.696 --> 00:08:22.735 line:0%
that we have seen in the lab,
and a control brown wood chip.

00:08:22.768 --> 00:08:24.637 align:start position:0% line:0%
-[Michael] Near each other?
-[Cecile] Yes, near each other.

00:08:24.670 --> 00:08:26.972
Aha, all right.

00:08:27.005 --> 00:08:28.874 align:start size:81% position:19%
-Let the games begin.
-Yeah.

00:08:28.907 --> 00:08:33.712 align:start size:94% position:6%
<i> For the first trial, Andrew
 places monkey chow on
 the control block of wood,</i>

00:08:33.745 --> 00:08:37.283
<i> the replica feces
