[Michael] They're looking...
now here comes one.

00:08:45.257 --> 00:08:46.825 align:start size:88% position:13%
-[Michael] No... oh, oh!
-[Cecile] Yeah.

00:08:46.858 --> 00:08:48.193 align:start position:0%
[Cecile]
No, he's smelling the wood chip.

00:08:48.226 --> 00:08:51.297 align:start position:0%
[Michael]
He smelled the wood chip,
the monkey chow fell off of it.

00:08:51.330 --> 00:08:53.299
[Cecile] Yes.

00:08:53.332 --> 00:08:56.302 align:start position:0%
[Michael]
Is he... gonna eat it?

