[Michael]
Shelled peanuts, okay.

00:09:10.749 --> 00:09:13.319 align:start size:78% position:22%
-[Cecile] So that's
on the fake poop.
-[Michael] Yep.

00:09:13.352 --> 00:09:15.621 align:start size:88% position:13%
-[Michael]
That's on the real poop.
-[Cecile] Yeah.

00:09:15.654 --> 00:09:18.190 align:start size:94% position:6%
-[Michael]
And that's on the wood block.
-[Cecile] Yes.

